p.k: A glimpse inside each Titan's dream world. / Robin tries to teach his superhero ways to Spanish speaking brothers Mas y Menos. / BB and Cyborg invite Starfire to join in their fun as long as she avoids dreaded uncle jokes. / Killer Moth offers a reward for Silkie's return, but will Silkier be happier away from the Titans? / Tired of Robin's bland cooking the other Titans try their hand at spicing up their food.
